msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/story"
msgid "Welcome to support weaponry training, Soldier.\n\n"
"In this tutorial, you will learn the basics of reinforcements. This includes calling in additional standard units and requesting support assets such as artillery and air strikes.\n\n"
"                                      Good luck!"
msgstr ""

